reviewText:
I got tired of this game right after finishing Green Hill Zone. Trust me when I say that this game tries way too hard to be like the old Sonic games, but now with:
- Screwed up physics;
- Boring gameplay;
- Ridiculous puzzles

And oh yeah... SONIC IS SLOWER THAN DOG SH*T.
Thank you SEGA <3

